* {{a|GenAm}} {{IPA|/bɚˈlɪnɚ/|lang=en}}
* {{a|RP}} {{IPA|/bəˈlɪnə/|lang=en}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A native or inhabitant of [[Berlin]].
